  <h1>Support</h1>
  <p class="sub">The Crib Shoes — Help & Contact</p>

  <div class="card">
    <p class="muted">
      For any questions or issues, please contact us at
      <strong><a href="mailto:support@yourdomain.com">support@yourdomain.com</a></strong>.
      We usually reply within 1–2 business days.
    </p>
  </div>

  <h2>Quick help</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Create an order:</strong> Open the app → <em>My Shoes</em> → <em>Request Cleaning</em> → choose cleaning type and pickup details.</li>
    <li><strong>Track status:</strong> <em>My Orders</em> shows live status: Created → Picked up → Cleaning → Done → Ready to deliver → Delivered.</li>
    <li><strong>Notifications:</strong> Enable push notifications in your phone settings to get status updates.</li>
    <li><strong>Addresses & payments:</strong> Update them in <em>Profile</em> → <em>Settings</em>.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Delete account</h2>
  <p>
    You can delete your account in the app: <em>Profile → Delete Account</em>.
    This permanently removes your profile and non-required data. Some records (e.g., invoices) may be retained where required by law.
  </p>

  <h2>Privacy</h2>
  <p>
    Read our <a href="https://alex5306467.github.io/crib-shoes/">Privacy Policy</a> to learn what data we collect and how we use it.
  </p>

  <hr>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
